{extends file="include/master.tpl"}

{block name=head}{/block}

{block name=body}

<div class="page-banner volunteer">
	<h1>Volunteer</h1>
</div>

<div class="container volunteer">

	<h2>100% Volunteer led - 100% Passion!</h2>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-3">
			<img class="img-responsive topic-icon" src="/assets/imgs/topic-icons/find-a-team.png" />
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-9">
			<p>As a community we love assisting young adults to explore, create and make magic happen.</p>
			<p>We love people who assist to make Dojos amazing and wonderful. Even if they don't know how to code, or how a computer works, we still love you to be involved to create magic.</p>
			<br />
			<a href="/volunteer/assist-a-dojo" class="btn btn-primary">Assist a Dojo</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<hr />
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-9">
			<p>Have some spare space? Part of an organisation that can donate an area for a few hours? We'd love you to provide the opportunity for CoderDojo ninjas to come together and create some magic together.</p>
			<br />
			<a href="/volunteer/create-a-dojo" class="btn btn-primary">Create a Dojo</a>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-3">			
			<img class="img-responsive topic-icon" src="/assets/imgs/topic-icons/find-a-team.png" />
		</div>
	</div>

	<hr />
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-3">			
			<img class="img-responsive topic-icon" src="/assets/imgs/topic-icons/find-a-venue.png" />
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-9">
			<p>Be part of the Community! It's always great to be around like minded individuals who enjoy assisting young adults to create their magic.</p>
			<br />
			<a href="/community" class="btn btn-primary">Be part of our Community</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
{/block}
